<p class="DNCBullet"><b>Trump&#8217;s Revised Tax Plan Would Cap Itemized Deductions For The Middle Class And Require More Low-Income Individuals To Pay Income Tax To Offset Lowering The Capital Gains Tax Rate And Expanding Itemized Deductions For Businesses.
